{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 56138, "create_time": 1647912879, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 0, "text": "[tmp]\n我觉得共产主义从道德上就是站不住脚的。资本家为打工人创造了就业岗位，承担了大部分市场风险，是市场创新的主体，资本家比打工人收入高不是天经地义的？高个几十倍稀松平常，高个几千几万倍也很合理，因为资本家组织生产创造的价值远高于打工人作为螺丝钉创造的价值。", "timestamp": 1647912879}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 56140, "create_time": 1647913041, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 0, "text": "[tmp]\n所以刘少奇在建国初期都说过“**剥削有功，剥削有理**”，正是有了所谓的“剥削”才有了社会的活力，甚至可以说“剥削”是推动社会进步的源动力。", "timestamp": 1647913041}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 56142, "create_time": 1647913202, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 0, "text": "[tmp]\n如果你们觉得工资低、压力大、福利差，不要怪资本家剥削了你，去找一份工资高、压力小、福利高的工作就是了，如果找不到，说明你们的能力就只值这个价钱。", "timestamp": 1647913202}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 56143, "create_time": 1647913209, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 0, "text": "[tmp]\n如果你们觉得不是自己的问题，是社会低估了你们，你们就自己做老板，为这个社会创造工作，养活你们的员工，体验剥削别人的感觉。", "timestamp": 1647913209}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 56145, "create_time": 1647913564, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "什么精神资本家，正常人应该是屁股在哪就站谁", "timestamp": 1647913564}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 56146, "create_time": 1647913682, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "啊对对对", "timestamp": 1647913682}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 56148, "create_time": 1647914106, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re Alice: 这下屁股了。汁人只用屁股不用脑袋思考社会公平，活该被图3kw", "timestamp": 1647914106}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 56156, "create_time": 1647915498, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "[![qK1xOJ.jpg](https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/03/22/qK1xOJ.jpg)](https://imgtu.com/i/qK1xOJ)", "timestamp": 1647915498}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 56160, "create_time": 1647915757, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 5, "text": "[tmp]\nRe Alice: 看到有大爹把土地分给自己就把“屁股”挪到大爹一边，过两年大爹把所有土地充公了，“屁股”却没地方挪了。", "timestamp": 1647915757}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 56171, "create_time": 1647916779, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "共产主义的精髓是按需分配。资本家组织生产为社会做出了贡献，就应该享受红酒牛排大豪斯。但问题是天天红酒牛排大豪斯一辈子能也花不了一个小目标，垄断更多的财富资源对资本家个人和家庭的生活质量并不会有更显著的提高。相反，把这些财富分给更多的打工人就可以让他们吃上10块钱炸鸡住上鸽子窝，小孩也能有学上以后有工打不至于沦为街溜子，对于社会长期的发展和稳定也是有利的。", "timestamp": 1647916779}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 56179, "create_time": 1647917473, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "Re Francis: 但是这不就是很多高福利国家的现状，所以他们才是共产主义？", "timestamp": 1647917473}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 56181, "create_time": 1647917564, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 8, "text": "[tmp]\n了解共产主义应该去看马克思，而不是看苏联或者中共的历史", "timestamp": 1647917564}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 56187, "create_time": 1647917811, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 9, "text": "Re Francis: 👍", "timestamp": 1647917811}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 56190, "create_time": 1647917877, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 10, "text": "#10897\n两个月之前发过一遍了，dz实在没活了可以咬打火机", "timestamp": 1647917877}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 56191, "create_time": 1647918041, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 11, "text": "Re 洞主: 任何阶级在一定时代条件下都有进步性，包括封建地主阶级，资产阶级当然也不例外，资本主义的发展确实很大程度上促进了生产力的发展。但与此同时还应当看到资本主义的剥削性，尤其是发展到金融资本主义的阶段，完全靠放贷收租模式赚钱，就变得阻碍生产力发展了", "timestamp": 1647918041}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 56192, "create_time": 1647918200, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 11, "text": "而资本主义的逐利性使得资本家们都会往垄断和金融资本主义的方向发展，也就是列宁所说的帝国主义。但是当资本家越来越富，工人越来越穷，工人甚至无法买得起自己生产的商品，这样就造成了商品过剩，引发经济危机，这是资本主义的内在矛盾，换句话说资本主义注定要自己毁灭自己", "timestamp": 1647918200}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 56193, "create_time": 1647918274, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 11, "text": "我国目前对实业资本持鼓励态度，原因就是dz所说的那几条，但对更高级形式的金融资本是充满警惕的（参考杰克马）。这就是我国还能自称社会主义的原因之一", "timestamp": 1647918274}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 56230, "create_time": 1647920341, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re Grace: 资本主义国家可以存在社会主义成分，同样的社会主义国家也有资本主义成分。", "timestamp": 1647920341}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 56251, "create_time": 1647921000, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 12, "text": "还是没穷过，你穷穷试试，你也给资本家打打工，看你还有机会从这上学没事发牢骚", "timestamp": 1647921000}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 56254, "create_time": 1647921379, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 13, "text": "[tmp]\nRe Louis: 还是没饿过，你饿饿试试，你也给大爹上缴上缴余粮，看你还有机会吃观音土以外的东西没事发牢骚。", "timestamp": 1647921379}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 56511, "create_time": 1647951734, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 14, "text": "Re Margaret: 啊对对对，没饿死你真是天大的罪过捏", "timestamp": 1647951734}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 56615, "create_time": 1647961785, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 12, "text": "Re Margaret: 啊对对对，没饿死你真是天大的罪过捏", "timestamp": 1647961785}], "create_time": 1647912781, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": true, "last_comment_time": 1647961785, "likenum": 18, "n_attentions": 18, "n_comments": 22, "pid": 20645, "poll": null, "reply": 22, "text": "[tmp]\n你们可以说我精资，但我还是完全get不到共产主义的point在哪啊\n---\n更理解不了这套意识形态为啥能在上个世纪吸引那么多人，甚至成为了我国的立国之本。", "timestamp": 1647912781}}